      <title>TikTok 难民在美测试习近平防火墙 拥抱中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/tiktok-refugees-in-us-test-xi-s-firewall-while-embracing-chinese</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席曾表示，人文交流是中美关系健康发展的基础。大量 TikTok“难民”涌入中国应用小红书，可能会考验习近平在这种非计划互动方面的极限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/tiktok-refugees-in-us-test-xi-s-firewall-while-embracing-chinese</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚在社交媒体上加强竞选规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/romania-toughens-campaign-rules-for-social-media-after-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚最高法院宣布去年总统选举结果无效后，该国即将批准针对 TikTok 和 Facebook 等社交媒体平台实施更严格的竞选规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/romania-toughens-campaign-rules-for-social-media-after-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 09:44:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政府将限制对企业的征税，重点关注对富人的征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/french-government-to-limit-levy-on-firms-focus-on-taxing-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预算部长阿梅莉·德蒙查兰表示，法国新政府计划将对企业的临时征税期限限制为一年，并将重点向富人征税，以寻求缩小赤字的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/french-government-to-limit-levy-on-firms-focus-on-taxing-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 09:05:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>八年的民粹主义并未让美国走多远</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-and-biden-s-economic-populism-isn-t-working-for-the-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以就业、财富或健康作为衡量标准，很难发现工人阶级有任何有意义的进步，这引发了人们对未来四年的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-and-biden-s-economic-populism-isn-t-working-for-the-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 09:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列指责哈马斯危及加沙停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/israel-says-hamas-creating-last-minute-crisis-halting-gaza-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡指责哈马斯违背了停火协议的部分内容，该协议原本有望暂停加沙地区持续 15 个多月的战斗，这使得这项期待已久的协议的完成面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/israel-says-hamas-creating-last-minute-crisis-halting-gaza-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 08:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回国前，库什纳获准在阿尔巴尼亚兴建豪华度假村</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/kushner-gets-approval-for-luxury-resort-project-in-albania-before-trump-s-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的女婿贾里德·库什纳已获得阿尔巴尼亚政府的初步批准，将在该国南部海岸外的一个岛屿上的前军事基地上建造一座价值 14 亿美元的豪华度假村。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/kushner-gets-approval-for-luxury-resort-project-in-albania-before-trump-s-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 08:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯声称破坏了乌克兰的天然气储存设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/russia-says-it-damaged-facilities-at-gas-storage-site-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯声称，在对乌克兰能源部门发动的一系列无人机和导弹袭击中，乌克兰利沃夫地区最大的天然气储存设施之一的地面基础设施遭到破坏。乌克兰称天然气供应并未中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/russia-says-it-damaged-facilities-at-gas-storage-site-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
