      <title>特朗普与丹麦总理通话时讨论格陵兰岛问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-discussed-greenland-interest-in-call-with-danish-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森周三与美国新任总统进行了 45 分钟的电话交谈后表示，唐纳德·特朗普证实他有意为美国收购格陵兰岛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-discussed-greenland-interest-in-call-with-danish-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 20:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
